name: Tunneled
description:
Tunneled is a unique endless runner game with a very satisfying and addictive gameplay. Survive and collect as many coins as you can. High quality graphics and music. Happy Gaming !!

It's completely ad free and intend to keep it like this.  Please donate if you like my work and want me to make more such free games. 

P.S. - This is a beta version. Login and Leaderboard functions won't work since those use Google Play Services. Please leave your feedback in comments. Happy Gaming !!
